-- own `natGcdFueled`. GAP-natToDecimal-wholeprogram (see the file header)
-- makes this genuinely infeasible even for this file's small result (`4`)
-- once the machinery is added to a program this file's own size --
-- confirmed empirically, not attempted here. Once resolved
-- (`wp/RTP1-interp-sharing`), the intended `main` is:
